{"type":"message","id":"16e3c438","parentId":"9d0c112e","timestamp":"2026-04-01T12:03:31.400Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个session只有一个消息，是我刚刚发出的查询请求。没有活跃的用户对话（只有机器人自己的工具调用）。让我再确认一下，可能需要查找真正的用户对话。\n\n从返回结果看，只有1个session，而且是\"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习\"这个定时任务本身，没有其他活跃的用户对话。\n\n让我执行自主学习任务 - 搜索道简网络相关行业的最新动态。","thinkingSignature":"4b44d6592b746c3636622d174e5a7daf5e30ed49998641571b39809c1b053c7e"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到没有用户活跃对话（只有当前定时任务自身），执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8b4azomohyxr_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":822,"output":136,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44939,"cost":{"input":0.0002466,"output":0.00016319999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00172923}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775045006155}}
{"type":"message","id":"e1f0ba6d","parentId":"16e3c438","timestamp":"2026-04-01T12:03:31.406Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8b4azomohyxr_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775045011403}}
{"type":"message","id":"06a53f98","parentId":"e1f0ba6d","timestamp":"2026-04-01T12:03:36.235Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要搜索道简网络相关行业的最新动态：企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等。让我执行多个搜索。","thinkingSignature":"e99494587248b60d955b712f5d4fd48b294802e47c931230c370238e106985a3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c7nvo1p2yf99_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新政策动态\" 2>/dev/null | head -100"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c7nvo1p2yf99_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业 2026发展趋势\" 2>/dev/null | head -100"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c7nvo1p2yf99_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 2026市场动态\" 2>/dev/null | head -100"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1473,"output":178,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45632,"cost":{"input":0.00044189999999999995,"output":0.0002136,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0019749299999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775045011406}}
